Package: rRINEX
Type: Package
Title: Reads RINEX Files
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Francesco",
             family = "Pirotti",
             role = c("cre", "aut"),
             email = "francesco.pirotti@unipd.it",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4796-6406") ) )
Maintainer: Francesco Pirotti <francesco.pirotti@unipd.it>
Description: Reads RINEX observation data, hooks up with 'RTKLIB'  (<http://www.rtklib.com/>) to use rnx2rtkp executable. Raw data and data-processing scripts are stored in the 'data-raw/' directory, which is not installed with the package.
